## Plotting helper

```matlab
figure('Name', 'Harmonic amplitudes');
n = size(amp_all, 1);
t = (0:size(amp_all,2)-1) / fs;

for row = 1:n
    subplot(n+1, 1, row);
    plot(t, amp_all(row,:));
    ylabel(freq_labels{row});
    grid on;
end
subplot(n+1, 1, n+1);
plot(t, phase_f1);
ylabel('Phase f_1 (rad)');  xlabel('Time (s)');
grid on;
```

