## Algorithm overview

```
sig  ──► [modwptdetails]  ──► WPT sub-bands
              │
              ▼  (bands at k·f1 and f2)
         [cwt per band]   ──► instantaneous amplitude  ──► amp_all

sig & fd ──► [wcoherence]  ──► cross-wavelet spectrum
                                      │
                                      ▼ (at f1)
                                   angle(·)  ──► phase_f1
```

Each long signal is processed in chunks of `ChunkSize` samples.  Each chunk is zero-padded by `Padding` samples on both sides before the transforms, and the padding region is discarded afterwards, minimising boundary artefacts.

